Why Angular?

Modular approach
re-usable code
development quicker and easier
usnit utestable
google+microsoft - here to stay.
makes use of typescript.


1/ is node installed?
>node -v


2/ npm -v


3/ ng --version


4/ create a new project:
>ng new <name of project>
>ng new hello-world

5/ cd into the project.
>cd hello-world

6/ run ngserver:
>ng server

might need to run:
>npm install


7/ create new component.
g=generate
c=component
>ng g c <name of component>
>ng g c test

8/ create a service
>ng g s <name of service>
>ng g s employee

is created inside the src->app folder







